WEBVTT

00:07.350 --> 00:09.116
If you were dating Wonder Woman

00:09.118 --> 00:11.852
and you had to break up with
her, how would you do it?

00:11.854 --> 00:13.519
Probably the most cowardly way possible,

00:13.521 --> 00:15.421
'cause she could snap
my neck in a heartbeat.

00:15.423 --> 00:17.590
Who has she dated in the
past? Like, has she dated?

00:17.592 --> 00:18.891
Steve Trevor?

00:18.893 --> 00:20.259
And who broke it off... Steve Trevor?

00:20.261 --> 00:21.294
- Yeah.
- How'd he do it?

00:21.296 --> 00:23.262
He faked his death.

00:25.553 --> 00:27.887
I think if it came to it, I
just wouldn't even fake it.

00:29.390 --> 00:32.958
I would just take the coward's way out.

00:32.960 --> 00:33.992
Well, how would you?

00:33.994 --> 00:35.227
I'd write her a letter.

00:35.229 --> 00:36.394
You know, who writes letters these days?

00:36.396 --> 00:37.996
A "Dear John" letter?

00:37.998 --> 00:39.631
I'd just... I'd be scared
to do it face-to-face.

00:39.633 --> 00:41.299
I'd definitely want
to be a fly on the wall

00:41.301 --> 00:42.734
as she read that letter.

00:42.736 --> 00:45.170
Like, "You've got to be kidding me.

00:45.172 --> 00:47.371
You've got to be kidding me."

00:47.373 --> 00:49.073
I've literally yet to meet the female

00:49.075 --> 00:51.308
that he's too good for.

00:51.310 --> 00:53.377
Like, suddenly it's Wonder Woman?

01:25.273 --> 01:27.261
Synced and Corrected by Nsiko 
